import { Box, Typography, Grid, Card, CardMedia, CardContent, Chip, Divider } from '@mui/material'
import { cofounders } from '../data/co-founders'

const AboutUs = () => (
  <Box
    id="about"
    sx={{
      position: 'relative',
      py: { xs: 8, md: 12 },
      px: { xs: 3, md: 10 },
      backgroundColor: '#F3E2D4',
      overflow: 'hidden',
    }}
  >
    {/* Faint diagonal stripes */}
    <Box
      sx={{
        position: 'absolute',
        top: 0, left: 0, right: 0, bottom: 0,
        backgroundImage: 'repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(65,94,114,0.05) 0 10px, transparent 10px 20px)',
        pointerEvents: 'none',
        zIndex: 0,
      }}
    />

    {/* Mission */}
    <Box sx={{ position: 'relative', zIndex: 1, mb: { xs: 6, md: 10 } }}>
      <Typography
        variant="h3"
        sx={{
          fontFamily: "'DM Serif Display', serif",
          fontWeight: 400,
          textAlign: 'center',
          color: '#17313E',
          mb: 2,
          '&:after': {
            content: '""',
            display: 'block',
            width: 60,
            height: 3,
            backgroundColor: '#415E72',
            mx: 'auto',
            mt: 1,
          },
        }}
      >
        Who We Are
      </Typography>
      <Grid container spacing={4} alignItems="center">
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Typography
            variant="h6"
            sx={{
              fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif',
              color: '#415E72',
              lineHeight: 1.6,
              mb: 3,
            }}
          >
            Odyssey of Wisdom is a youth association based in Ancient Olympia, dedicated to empowering Greek youth from underserved areas by opening doors to Erasmus+ opportunities in Europe. We believe in connecting young people with life-changing experiences through travel, learning, and intercultural exchange.
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="body1"
            sx={{
              fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif',
              color: '#17313E',
              lineHeight: 1.7,
            }}
          >
            Our founders grew up in rural Greece and understand the barriers faced by youth with fewer resources. From Armenia to the Canary Islands, their Erasmus+ journeys inspired this initiativeâ€”to help others expand their horizons and grow as global citizens.
          </Typography>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Box
            component="img"
            src="/assets/olympia.jpg"      // Replace with a contextual photo
            alt="Ancient Olympia"
            sx={{
              width: '100%',
              borderRadius: 3,
              boxShadow: '0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)',
            }}
          />
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>

    <Divider sx={{ borderColor: '#C5B0CD', mb: { xs: 6, md: 10 } }} />

    {/* Vision & Activities */}
    <Box sx={{ position: 'relative', zIndex: 1, mb: { xs: 6, md: 10 } }}>
      <Typography
        variant="h4"
        sx={{
          fontFamily: "'DM Serif Display', serif",
          fontWeight: 400,
          textAlign: 'center',
          color: '#17313E',
          mb: 3,
        }}
      >
        Our Vision & Activities
      </Typography>
      <Grid container spacing={2} justifyContent="center" mb={4}>
        {[
          'Soft Skills',
          'AI & Innovation',
          'Sustainability',
          'Active Citizenship',
          'European Identity',
          'Media & Communication',
          'Entrepreneurship',
          'Environment',
          'Leadership',
          'Nonâ€‘formal Learning',
          'Intercultural Dialogue',
          'Sports',
        ].map((topic) => (
          <Grid item key={topic}>
            <Chip
              label={topic}
              sx={{
                backgroundColor: '#415E72',
                color: '#F3E2D4',
                fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif',
                fontWeight: 500,
                px: 2,
                py: 1,
                borderRadius: '16px',
              }}
            />
          </Grid>
        ))}
      </Grid>
      <Typography
        variant="body1"
        sx={{
          fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif',
          color: '#17313E',
          textAlign: 'center',
          maxWidth: 800,
          mx: 'auto',
          lineHeight: 1.7,
        }}
      >
        From local workshops in Ancient Olympia to international exchanges, we focus on nurturing skills, fostering unity, and promoting European values. We envision a network of youth connected like dots in a vibrant patternâ€”learning, sharing, and giving back.
      </Typography>
    </Box>

    <Divider sx={{ borderColor: '#C5B0CD', mb: { xs: 6, md: 10 } }} />

    {/* Founders */}
    <Box sx={{ position: 'relative', zIndex: 1 }}>
      <Typography
        variant="h4"
        sx={{
          fontFamily: "'DM Serif Display', serif",
          fontWeight: 400,
          textAlign: 'center',
          color: '#17313E',
          mb: 3,
        }}
      >
        Meet the Founders
      </Typography>
      <Typography
        variant="body1"
        sx={{
          fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif',
          color: '#415E72',
          textAlign: 'center',
          maxWidth: 900,
          mx: 'auto',
          mb: 6,
        }}
      >
        A dynamic team of students and young professionals across disciplinesâ€”united by a passion for youth empowerment and cultural exchange.
      </Typography>
      <Grid container spacing={6} justifyContent="center">
        {cofounders.map((person) => (
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} key={person.name}>
            <Card
              elevation={3}
              sx={{
                maxWidth: 300,
                mx: 'auto',
                transition: 'transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease',
                '&:hover': { transform: 'translateY(-6px)', boxShadow: '0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15)' },
              }}
            >
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                image={person.image}
                alt={person.name}
                sx={{
                  height: 300,
                  objectFit: 'cover',
                  borderTopLeftRadius: 8,
                  borderTopRightRadius: 8,
                }}
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography
                  variant="h6"
                  sx={{
                    fontFamily: "'DM Serif Display', serif",
                    mb: 1,
                    color: '#17313E',
                  }}
                >
                  {person.name}
                </Typography>
                <Chip
                  label={person.role}
                  size="small"
                  sx={{
                    backgroundColor: '#415E72',
                    color: 'white',
                    mb: 1,
                    fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif',
                  }}
                />
                <Typography
                  variant="body2"
                  color="text.secondary"
                  sx={{
                    fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif',
                    display: '-webkit-box',
                    WebkitBoxOrient: 'vertical',
                    WebkitLineClamp: 4,
                    overflow: 'hidden',
                    textOverflow: 'ellipsis',
                  }}
                >
                  {person.bio}
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        ))}
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  </Box>
)

export default AboutUs
